intro: Meet the new kind of UFO!
description:
Take control of a new kind of UFO - the Builder! There is nothing to destroy or steal. On the contrary, you can help Earthlings build or rebuild their homes.  

Fly to construction sites and use the capabilities of your futuristic ships to help. Each house is different, and you must rebuild them piece by piece. Imagine the surprise and gratitude of the inhabitants for such help! 

Besides building - defend your buildings from enemies who want to interfere with you and try to destroy them.    

Check out the new fun game from the NOSTRA.GAMES team. 

UFO not only destroy - they can help build!
